1. *Spasio* ga je u poslednji čas. (He was saved at the last minute.)
2. Ona je *spasila* njegov život. (She saved his life.)
3. *Spasiti* ću te, obećavam. (I will save you, I promise.)
4. On je *spasio* sebe od tuče. (He saved himself from the fight.)
5. Oni su *spasili* malu decu. (They saved a small child.)
6. *Spasen* je u poslednji čas. (He was saved at the last minute.) 
7. Ona je *spasena* od opasnosti. (She was saved from danger.) 
8. On je *spasen* od smrti. (He was saved from death.)